  }))), "Trivial"), mdx("p", null, "Thanks to the re-release in South Korea, I saw Fury Road and Furiosa in theaters around the same time. I watched Fury Road at an extended-screen cinema, which perfectly matched the film's linearity. I felt overwhelmed without a moment's rest, leaving me utterly drained."), mdx("p", null, "I wished it had the grainy film texture of Fury Road. It felt less logical for a prequel to have crisper visuals."), mdx("p", null, "Since Furiosa was essentially the main character of Fury Road, Max's role seemed diminished, making me wish for a sequel. However, with the global box office flop, the production of the third film seems uncertain."));
